村，香港歷史可以追溯到二千年前南粵國時期，歷史文化同民俗悠久得多。構成現代支那雜種如斯民族最早只可追溯到清帝國，所以點解蝗話英文叫mandarin正是支共出現之前洋人對支那嘅講法，因此香港不論在民族歷史抑或民俗、文化、語言都比支那更悠久更出色，支那班蟎蝴漢雜種論歷史論語言有乜資格出聲"},{"pid":"75653a96746a5ce835a00249cb8ca9c8b046f57e","tid":398533,"uid":131205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根據佢地既偉論，歷史上獨立左既國家點解又獨立到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬來西亞都係中國既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢哋遲早會話馬來西亞自古以來係中國不可分裂嘅一部份，<br />\n班友係咁厚臉皮。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟據此邏輯，遲早要話<br />\n美國自古以來係中國不可分裂嘅一部份，<br />\n非洲自古以來係中國不可分裂的一部份，<br />\n全世界自古以來係中國不可分裂的一部份<br />\n<br />\n因為唔知幾多十億年前全世界大陸係連埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0761b57218b048a27bb228cf963872b9c99957","tid":398533,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"13億人講胡言亂語<br />\n結論係嗰13億唔係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773979f40c60a50ba7fe5b5d39f72a578d1f4568","tid":398533,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eddec839ce8965203b35be375d8a562505c117f5","tid":398533,"uid":80535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個Post d本土/港獨狗又搬龍門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦5毛"},{"pid":"5d1ecc023098867b97170eaafe0e33d9ba55b99d","tid":398533,"uid":86841,"lik